    <section class="md:px-10 md:py-40 bg-ltrn-lighter" id="assessment-points">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class={[
          "flex items-center gap-4 py-4 px-10 md:px-4 border-b-2 border-ltrn-primary font-display font-black text-lg",
          "md:inline-flex md:border-2 md:rounded-full"
        ]}>
          1. <span class="w-[2px] self-stretch bg-ltrn-primary" />
          Assessment points, feedback, and comments tracking
        </h2>
        <div class={[
          "max-w-md px-10 pb-40 mt-10 text-xl",
          "md:px-0 md:pb-0"
        ]}>
          <p>Assessment points are Lanttern's core elements.</p>
          <br />
          <p>
            They are always linked to learning contexts (strands or activities), curriculum, and can be enriched with comments and feedback — allowing students and educators to explore learning patterns, discuss about learning strategies, and reflect on teaching practices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="md:px-10 md:py-40" id="differentiation">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class={[
          "flex items-center gap-4 py-4 px-10 md:px-4 border-b-2 border-ltrn-primary font-display font-black text-lg",
          "md:inline-flex md:border-2 md:rounded-full"
        ]}>
          2. <span class="w-[2px] self-stretch bg-ltrn-primary" /> Differentiation and inclusion
        </h2>
        <div class={[
          "px-10 pb-40 mt-10 text-xl",
          "md:px-0 md:pb-0"
        ]}>
          <p>
            Every brain is unique.<br /> Every student has a unique learning path.<br />
            Diversity and inclusion are key for a 21st century education.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Lanttern encourages an individualized and inclusive education approach by providing support to assessment and curriculum adaptation, differentiation rubrics, and special needs pedagogical documentation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="md:px-10 md:py-40 bg-ltrn-lighter" id="planning">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class={[
          "flex items-center gap-4 py-4 px-10 md:px-4 border-b-2 border-ltrn-primary font-display font-black text-lg",
          "md:inline-flex md:border-2 md:rounded-full"
        ]}>
