        </h2>
        <div class={[
          "px-10 pb-40 mt-10 text-xl",
          "md:px-0 md:pb-0"
        ]}>
          <p>Lanttern uses strands and activities to give context to learning.</p>
          <br />
          <p>
            We help teachers and educational designers in making their intentions visible through pedagogical documentation, enabling deep conversations about teaching practices in the school community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="md:px-10 md:py-40" id="curriculum">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class={[
          "flex items-center gap-4 py-4 px-10 md:px-4 border-b-2 border-ltrn-primary font-display font-black text-lg",
          "md:inline-flex md:border-2 md:rounded-full"
